35:16.157 --> 35:19.160
♪ Oh, what can it mean ♪

35:19.160 --> 35:22.816
♪ To a daydream believer ♪

35:22.816 --> 35:25.253
♪ And a home...♪

35:57.024 --> 35:58.025
Where is Autje?

35:59.548 --> 36:01.855
Well, we must
begin without her.

36:05.206 --> 36:06.164
Thank you.

36:07.991 --> 36:09.645
Were you smoking?

36:09.645 --> 36:10.907
Is that any of your business?

36:10.907 --> 36:12.126
Please.

36:16.739 --> 36:19.481
I can't live
a second longer!

36:19.481 --> 36:20.787
Autje!

36:27.141 --> 36:28.621
-  Autje!

36:32.102 --> 36:33.713
Autje, wait until
I get ahold of you.

36:35.105 --> 36:36.672
The census taker just told us

36:36.672 --> 36:37.760
that one of our men
is returning

36:37.760 --> 36:40.502
from the city late tonight.

36:40.502 --> 36:42.461
They need more bail money
for the attackers.

36:42.461 --> 36:43.549
Which man?

36:45.072 --> 36:46.160
Your Klaas.

36:47.335 --> 36:49.250
So time
is of the essence.

36:49.250 --> 36:50.947
Everyone get back
to your seats.

36:54.212 --> 36:56.562
August, please,
pros for leaving.

36:57.650 --> 36:59.173
Pros for leaving.

37:02.220 --> 37:04.047
We will be gone.

37:04.047 --> 37:05.440
We will be safe.

37:05.440 --> 37:06.702
Maybe not.

37:06.702 --> 37:08.095
The first is most
definitely a fact,

37:08.095 --> 37:09.662
that if we leave
we will be gone.

37:09.662 --> 37:11.838
Do we really need to state
the obvious over and over?

37:13.492 --> 37:14.667
Yes, Autje.

37:15.929 --> 37:18.497
We will see
a bit of the world.

37:18.497 --> 37:20.020
Let's move on
to the cons of leaving.

37:20.020 --> 37:21.151
We, the women, will decide

37:21.151 --> 37:23.023
what happens
in these meetings.

37:24.242 --> 37:26.896
Not a two-bit failed farmer
who must teach.

37:26.896 --> 37:28.637
You have been invited here.

37:28.637 --> 37:30.291
You have been invited
here to listen

37:30.291 --> 37:32.859
to what we have to say
and write it down.

37:32.859 --> 37:35.731
Nothing more.
Just listen.

37:35.731 --> 37:37.342
Mariche!

37:37.342 --> 37:40.910
Klaas will be returning soon
and you are wasting time.

37:40.910 --> 37:42.912
He will come to your house
just long enough

37:42.912 --> 37:46.394
to take his animals in order
to sell for bail money

37:46.394 --> 37:49.397
that will see the rapists
return to the colony

37:49.397 --> 37:50.833
and he will lay his hands

37:50.833 --> 37:53.619
on you and on your children.

37:53.619 --> 37:56.535
And you, as always,
do nothing,

37:56.535 --> 37:59.799
but fire away at us
with all of this rage.

38:02.105 --> 38:03.542
I would like to apologize

38:03.542 --> 38:05.761
for wrongly attempting
to nudge the proceedings.

38:07.546 --> 38:09.025
That's not my place.

38:14.161 --> 38:15.380
Mejal!

38:20.733 --> 38:21.908
I'll stop.

38:23.344 --> 38:24.780
Mama.

38:29.350 --> 38:31.657
What's the matter?
What's the matter?

38:33.049 --> 38:34.573
What is it? Hmm?

38:38.185 --> 38:39.926
Miep, what is it?

38:41.014 --> 38:42.798
I hurt.

38:45.888 --> 38:47.194
It's all right.

38:49.631 --> 38:50.980
It's all right.

38:57.770 --> 38:59.075
It's all right.

39:06.039 --> 39:08.215
There are no cons of leaving.

39:10.391 --> 39:12.045
It's all right.

39:16.223 --> 39:18.268
Not to worry, Nettie.

